\\mathbf{e}_{\\mathbf{k} s} \\hat{a}_{\\mathbf{k} s}(t)", "state" -> "Boxes"|>,
  "TeXAssistantTemplate"]], "Input",
 CellID->551294123,ExpressionUUID->"a3b02e83-57e4-e745-8cdb-590d09057e50"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Assuming the atom is in some initial state ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"|", "g"}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "4617b42e-5d55-a749-86e6-4848fab6fdf9"],
 " and transitions to a ionized atomic state",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"|", "e"}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "21585f11-6839-f54c-bbca-ac230515b38f"],
 ", and the field transitions to some state ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"|", "i"}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "9c67446e-10ff-7f4e-8485-2bb7ad6c7912"],
 " to ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"|", "f"}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "d5a9bb3f-5797-2b43-b238-3f7908f18b8c"],
 ". Letting ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"|", "I"}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], " ", "=", 
       RowBox[{"|", "g"}]}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], " ", "|", "i"}], 
    "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "69efa624-ba8f-5c43-be50-0bbd6d52c70b"],
 " and ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"|", "F"}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], " ", "=", " ", 
       RowBox[{"|", "e"}]}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], " ", "|", "g"}], 
    "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "e8e741bc-70c3-0a4b-8519-d7050e397032"],
 " the transition probability for the full system is ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"|", 
    RowBox[{"\[LeftAngleBracket]", 
     RowBox[{"F", "|", 
      SuperscriptBox["H", 
       RowBox[{"(", "I", ")"}]], "|", "I"}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], 
    SuperscriptBox["|", "2"]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "3518028f-e603-4342-b8f4-c9739e792fc6"],
 ", and for the field is ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"|", 
    RowBox[{"\[LeftAngleBracket]", 
     RowBox[{"f", "|", 
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox["E", 
        RowBox[{"(", "+", ")"}]], "(", 
       RowBox[{
        StyleBox["r",
         FontWeight->"Bold"], ",", "t"}], ")"}], "|", "i"}], 
     "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], 
    SuperscriptBox["|", "2"]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "9e3554aa-5a75-0948-ad93-04146f88954e"],
 ". We only care about the final state of the detector not the field, so we \
have to sum over all the states ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"|", "f"}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "cb8765d4-36ce-6544-a23b-530ec98d3aac"],
 " which without loss of generality assume to be complete"
}], "Text",
 CellID->11138904,ExpressionUUID->"517588f3-9bb5-9c4f-b2ab-b343bd7c6186"],

Cell["Performing the sum we get:", "Text",
 CellID->158135442,ExpressionUUID->"e0a4ec5e-2a6c-bc4c-a4ef-8257365a2032"],

